<tr>
<th scope="row">Subject</th>
<td colspan="3">21,000 International Patients Chose Korea for Medical Treatment in 2013</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Date</th>
<td>2014-05-21</td>
<th scope="row">Hit</th>
<td>3971</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Contents</th>
<td class="view" colspan="3"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><u><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">21,000 International Patients Chose Korea for Medical Treatment in 2013 <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></u></b></p>
<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><u><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">(650,000 foreign patients’ visitations to hospitals)<o:p></o:p></font></font></span></u></b></p>
<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">- Generated 393.4 billion won in patient service revenues in 2013 -<o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">- A total of 630,000 international patients visited Korea for medical service over five years since 2009, generating 950 million dollars in patient service revenues -<o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">- The number of foreign patients entering Korea for medical treatment increased by 32.5 percent year-on-year (The number of patients’ visit to hospital jumped 36.9 percent) -<o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">In 2013, a total of approximately 210,000 international patients visited Korea for medical services, generating around 400 billion won in patient service revenues.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">Ministry of Health and Welfare (Minister Moon Hyung-pyo) stated that the analysis of data submitted by medical institutes registered for attracting international patients indicated that 211,218 foreign patients from 191 countries visited Korea for medical services in 2013. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; line-height: 160%; text-indent: -42.9pt; margin: 5pt 0cm 0pt 42.9pt; background: white; vertical-align: baseline; mso-pagination: none">
<font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 160%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; background: white; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko; mso-bidi-language: ar-sa">&lt; (2009-2013) Foreign Patients Visiting Korea</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 160%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko; mso-bidi-language: ar-sa"> [Unit: person, %] &gt;<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<div align="center">
<table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="MsoNormalTable" style="border-bottom: medium none; border-left: medium none; border-collapse: collapse; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .25pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid black .25pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid black .25pt; mso-table-overlap: never; mso-yfti-tbllook: 1184">
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 204.5pt; mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes">
<td style="border-bottom: black 1pt solid; border-left: black 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 1.4pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.1pt; width: 374.35pt; padding-right: 5.1pt; height: 204.5pt; border-top: black 1pt solid; border-right: black 1pt solid; padding-top: 1.4pt; mso-border-alt: solid black .25pt" width="499">
<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; line-height: 160%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-pagination: none">
<font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 160%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt; mso-fareast-language: ko; mso-fareast-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-language: ar-sa; mso-no-proof: yes"><v:shapetype coordsize="21600,21600" filled="f" id="_x0000_t75" o:preferrelative="t" o:spt="75" path="m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe" stroked="f"><v:stroke joinstyle="miter"></v:stroke><v:formulas><v:f eqn="if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0"></v:f><v:f eqn="sum @0 1 0"></v:f><v:f eqn="sum 0 0 @1"></v:f><v:f eqn="prod @2 1 2"></v:f><v:f eqn="prod @3 21600 pixelWidth"></v:f><v:f eqn="prod @3 21600 pixelHeight"></v:f><v:f eqn="sum @0 0 1"></v:f><v:f eqn="prod @6 1 2"></v:f><v:f eqn="prod @7 21600 pixelWidth"></v:f><v:f eqn="sum @8 21600 0"></v:f><v:f eqn="prod @7 21600 pixelHeight"></v:f><v:f eqn="sum @10 21600 0"></v:f></v:formulas><v:path gradientshapeok="t" o:connecttype="rect" o:extrusionok="f"></v:path><o:lock aspectratio="t" v:ext="edit"></o:lock></v:shapetype><v:shape alt="EMB00000fec10db" id="_x143589576" o:spid="_x0000_i1026" style="width: 305.25pt; height: 199.5pt; visibility: visible; mso-wrap-style: square" type="#_x0000_t75"><v:imagedata o:title="EMB00000fec10db" src="file:///C:\Users\Mohw-UP\AppData\Local\Temp\msohtmlclip1\01\clip_image001.png"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 160%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt; mso-fareast-language: ko; mso-fareast-font-family: 굴림; mso-bidi-language: ar-sa"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#000000">(Nationality) <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>In terms of patient nationality, China topped the list, followed by America, Russia, Japan and Mongolia. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -7.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 7.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.59">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#000000">- In particular, Russia ranked the third in the number of foreign patients visiting Korea for medical treatments. 240,000 Russian patients travelled to Korea in 2013, which was a 46 percent jump on-year. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -7.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 7.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.59">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#000000">- Patients from the UAE jumped 237 percent to 1,151 in 2013 from 342 in the previous year thanks to the patient exchange agreement entered between Korea and the UAE. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 14.15pt; mso-char-indent-count: -1.18">
<font color="#000000"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'times new roman'"><font face="맑은 고딕">※</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font face="Times New Roman"> Average medical expense per patient in the UAE costs 17.71 million won, which is 9.5 times higher than 1.86 million won of the medical expenses a foreign patient pays on average for medical service in Korea.<o:p></o:p></font></span></font></p>
<p>
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-language: en-us; mso-ansi-language: en-us"><br clear="all" style="page-break-before: always"/>
</span></p>
<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#000000">&lt; UAE Patient Treatment Cases under the Patient Exchange Program &gt;<o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><v:shapetype coordsize="21600,21600" id="_x0000_t202" o:spt="202" path="m,l,21600r21600,l21600,xe"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#000000"><v:stroke joinstyle="miter"></v:stroke><v:path gradientshapeok="t" o:connecttype="rect"></v:path></font></font></v:shapetype><v:shape id="_x0000_s1026" style="width: 441.7pt; height: 313.95pt; mso-height-percent: 200; mso-left-percent: -10001; mso-top-percent: -10001; mso-position-horizontal: absolute; mso-position-horizontal-relative: char; mso-position-vertical: absolute; mso-position-vertical-relative: line; mso-width-relative: margin; mso-height-relative: margin" type="#_x0000_t202"><v:textbox style="mso-fit-shape-to-text: t">
<p>
		 </p>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: #000000; border-left: #000000; background-color: transparent; border-top: #000000; border-right: #000000">
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#000000">(Case 1) Mr. A suffering from end-stage renal disease was admitted to Seoul National University Hospital in December 2013 upon the recommendation by the UAE military and received a kidney transplant before being discharged. Three years ago, he had a coronary artery bypass surgery and a percutaneous coronary intervention to treat his ischemic heart disease and he had been rejected by a university hospital in China for kidney transplantation. He is now receiving treatment as an outpatient and is recuperating without developing any complications. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font face="Times New Roman">(Case 2) Members of the B Family who came to Korea by referral from the Abu Dhabi health authority to treat their daughter suffering from neurocytoma ended up being treated at the Seoul Saint Mary’s Hospital. Mr. B who came to Seoul Saint Mary’s Hospital in January 2013 for the treatment of his three-year old daughter C suddenly had an acute chest pain and was admitted to the infectious disease ward for treatment while his wife who had been receiving pre-natal care since arriving Korea had a cesarean operation to give birth to a baby girl in September 2013. Their daughter C received anti-cancer treatment and autologous BMT twice, and went under a surgery to remove tumors. The B family returned to Abu Dhabi in March 2013 temporarily before starting to receive treatment at the end of April.</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-language: ko"><font face="맑은 고딕"><font size="3"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">    </span><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></font></p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</v:textbox><w:wrap type="none"></w:wrap><w:anchorlock></w:anchorlock></v:shape></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p>
	 </p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -7.05pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 7.05pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.64">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">- Patients from countries, such as Kazakhstan, Mongolia and Uzbekistan, with which Korea is continuing to build cooperation, are on the rise.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">(Medical Service Revenues) <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>Revenues generated from treating international patients amounted to 393.4 billion won, up 47 percent from the 267.3 billion won in 2012. <o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -7.05pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 7.05pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.64">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">- Average medical service cost per patient is 1.86 million won (10.7 percent increase year-on-year), 1.8 times higher than the 1.02 million won a Korean spends a year on average.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">- Patients who spend over 100 million won rose 43 percent year on year, reaching 117. <o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -7.05pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 7.05pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.64">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">- Chinese patients spent the most for medical services in Korea with 101.6 billion won, followed by Russian patients who spent 89.9 billion won. <o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -7.05pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 7.05pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.64">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">- In terms of medical service cost per patient, patients from the UAE spent the most with 17.71 million won, followed by patients from Kazakhstan with 4.56 million won.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">(Treatment Type) <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>Foreign inpatients totaled 20,137 in 2013, showing an annual average growth rate of 51 percent since 2009, while the average number of days a patient is admitted to a hospital was 12.3 days. <o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">(Contributing Factors for the Increase in International Patients) <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>More patients from China and Russia (an increase of over 300,000 patients from China and Russia accounted for 60 percent of the total increase) contributed to the increase of 50,000 international patients in 2013 compared to the previous year. <o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -7.05pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 7.05pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.64">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">- Chinese patients preferred to visit physicians specializing in plastics, dermatology and internal medicine, while Russian patients came to Korea for medical check-ups, and for medical treatment at internal medicine, obstetrics, general surgery or dermatology departments. <o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">Since 2009 when medical treatment for foreign patients was selected as a new growth engine, the accumulative number of international patients travelling to Korea for medical patients surpassed 630,000 and they spent approximately 1 trillion won in medical expenses. <o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">Considering that 2014 is the first year for Korea to take a quantum leap forward in attracting 1 million international patients by 2020, the Ministry of Health and Welfare will do its best to provide full support for the goal accomplishment. <o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -7.05pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 7.05pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.64">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; mso-fareast-language: ko"><font size="3"><font color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman">- The Ministry will continue to strengthen government-to-government (G2G) cooperation in the area of medical services, and augment the infrastructure necessary for attracting international patients, such as promoting Korean medical services aboard, offering training programs for foreign physicians, and developing medical volunteer programs. <o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p>
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-language: ko; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-language: en-us; mso-ansi-language: en-us"><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman">- In addition, the Ministry will make efforts to diversify channels for attracting international patients such as helping local medical institutes set up overseas branches, and opening or increasing a number of pre-post care centers. At the same time, the government will establish market order by cracking down on illegal medical practices offered to foreigners. </font></span></p></td>
</tr>
